# suiteNames

**Instance Property**

Returns the names of the suite definitions currently loaded by the application.

## Declaration

```swift
var suiteNames: [String] { get }
```

## Getting Suite Information

- **suite(forAppleEventCode:)**: Returns the name of the suite definition associated with the given four-character Apple event code, `code`.
